===== Installation des plugins nagios =====


<code>
./install -p nagios-plugins
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Install nagios plugins
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 > installing prerequisites
 > Extract archive content
 > Configure source tree
 > Building ....
 > Installing
</code>

